page_title: What's new in Azure OpenAI Service?
page_description: Learn about the latest news and features updates for Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: August 2023### Azure OpenAI on your own data (preview) updates- You can now deploy Azure OpenAI On Your Data to Power Virtual Agents.- Azure OpenAI On Your Data now supports private endpoints.- Ability to filter access to sensitive documents.- Automatically refresh your index on a schedule.- Vector search and semantic search options. - View your chat history in the deployed web app
